Dragon Scale Mail (DSM)
-----------------------

All dragon scale mail has the ability to ignore fire, cold, acid, and
lightning, and is not damaged or destroyed by such elemental attacks.  All
dragon armor even if normal has a base enchantment of +10, except for power
dragon scale mail which has a base enchantment of +15.  All DSM can be
thrown to inflict 2d4 points of damage.

All dragon armor may be periodically activated for a breath attack
corresponding to the type of dragon armor; all of these attacks have a
radius of 2 and do the indicated amount of damage at the center of the
blast.  (If more than one damage type is listed, the attack type is chosen
at random from the list.)  Once so activated, the DSM needs to recharge for
